WEBVTT

01:37.940 --> 01:41.020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

01:41.060 --> 01:43.979
[Episode 4]

01:46.000 --> 01:47.070
Sign this before you leave.

01:47.070 --> 01:47.950
You're really going to do this?

01:47.950 --> 01:48.970
I've already signed it.

01:48.970 --> 01:50.900
All that's left is your signature.

01:56.030 --> 01:57.570
I'll sign it when I get to the office.

01:57.570 --> 01:59.710
I'll give it back to you tonight.

02:06.600 --> 02:08.400
Lu Zhenzhen, why are you hiding?

02:08.960 --> 02:09.820
I'm not hiding.

02:10.169 --> 02:12.000
I'm leaving out of respect for you.

02:12.000 --> 02:13.240
Out of respect for me?

02:13.430 --> 02:14.830
That sounds like

02:14.910 --> 02:16.590
I'm the mistress.

02:16.590 --> 02:17.960
You've had too much. Let's go back.

02:17.960 --> 02:18.800
I haven't even had a drink yet.

02:18.800 --> 02:19.600
How am I drunk?

02:19.960 --> 02:20.750
Let go of me.

02:20.770 --> 02:21.820
Let go of me!

02:21.870 --> 02:23.130
What's wrong with you?

02:23.440 --> 02:25.700
You're scared, aren't you, Nie Yucheng?

02:26.550 --> 02:28.790
That's you in the video, right?

02:29.020 --> 02:30.900
It's not some AI face swap, right?

02:33.280 --> 02:33.960
It's me.

02:34.160 --> 02:36.130
At a critical time like this,

02:36.150 --> 02:37.920
you're still making trouble for yourself?

02:37.920 --> 02:39.790
Have you lost your mind?

02:40.329 --> 02:41.520
I don't know why she suddenly...

02:41.520 --> 02:43.150
Your promotion to Vice President

02:43.150 --> 02:45.000
was supposed to be announced this week.

02:45.000 --> 02:46.420
Now it's suddenly on hold,

02:46.420 --> 02:48.280
and the group is calling about it.

02:51.960 --> 02:54.280
You usually seem quite smart.

02:54.280 --> 02:55.280
How could you, at such a critical moment,

02:55.280 --> 02:57.150
do such a stupid thing?

02:57.210 --> 02:59.590
You're just giving them ammo, aren't you?

03:00.160 --> 03:01.030
I don't know why

03:01.030 --> 03:02.520
things turned out like this.

03:02.520 --> 03:03.650
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

03:03.650 --> 03:06.250
Go back right now and sort this out.

03:06.560 --> 03:09.860
Deal with your personal scandals.

03:09.980 --> 03:10.910
Stop messing around.

03:10.910 --> 03:12.000
At the corporate group,

03:12.000 --> 03:14.680
I've said all the good things
I could for you.

03:14.680 --> 03:17.070
But now that this matter has spread,

03:17.150 --> 03:19.430
your promotion will definitely be delayed.

03:19.430 --> 03:22.340
Whether you get it in the end
depends on your luck.

03:23.360 --> 03:24.910
I'll deal with it immediately.

03:24.910 --> 03:25.910
Thank you, Mr. Hu.

03:42.870 --> 03:43.079
[Divorce Agreement]

03:43.500 --> 03:45.250
[Husband's fingerprint]
[Wife's fingerprint] [Xu Miyu]

03:49.340 --> 03:50.600
Why didn't you sign it?

03:56.090 --> 03:57.370
I'm sorry, Miyu.

04:00.380 --> 04:02.370
I went too far that day.

04:03.260 --> 04:04.810
I didn't really mean it,

04:05.470 --> 04:07.710
but I hurt you in a moment of impulse.

04:08.670 --> 04:10.070
I hope you can forgive me.

04:15.830 --> 04:17.490
I really don't want a divorce.

04:17.810 --> 04:18.690
Miyu,

04:19.130 --> 04:20.160
I love you.

04:20.480 --> 04:21.680
I swear to you,

04:22.089 --> 04:22.930
this time,

04:23.950 --> 04:26.280
I will make a clean break
with Lu Zhenzhen.

04:26.680 --> 04:28.480
I won't do anything to hurt you.

04:28.860 --> 04:29.920
Please believe me.

04:33.659 --> 04:35.130
Do you not want a divorce,

04:35.720 --> 04:37.720
or do you just not want one right now?

04:40.000 --> 04:41.330
What do you mean by that?

04:41.750 --> 04:43.040
I heard

04:44.360 --> 04:46.960
your promotion
to vice president got delayed.

04:47.560 --> 04:49.960
Are you waiting until after your promotion

04:50.220 --> 04:51.620
to finalize the divorce?

05:01.480 --> 05:02.970
You can't be serious, Xu Miyu.

05:02.970 --> 05:04.700
Do you really hate me that much?

05:05.400 --> 05:07.530
Are you just bent on ruining my career?

05:08.750 --> 05:09.630
Anyway,

05:09.630 --> 05:10.980
we were husband and wife.

05:10.980 --> 05:12.910
You turn against me just like that.

05:12.950 --> 05:14.950
Don't you care about our past at all?

05:16.370 --> 05:18.440
You are exaggerating, Nie Yucheng.

05:18.550 --> 05:19.230
Me,

05:19.930 --> 05:21.500
ruin your future?

05:22.210 --> 05:24.490
At most, I can delay it for a year or so.

05:24.610 --> 05:26.420
As for the past you mentioned,

05:27.290 --> 05:28.820
after 10 years of marriage,

05:29.780 --> 05:31.750
I'm the one who truly has no way out.

05:32.450 --> 05:34.350
If I really take another step back,

05:34.350 --> 05:35.890
then I would really become

05:35.920 --> 05:37.450
the parasite you called me.

05:38.570 --> 05:40.210
Living off the job you gave me

05:40.760 --> 05:42.360
without any dignity.

05:42.720 --> 05:43.740
Every day feels like having

05:43.740 --> 05:45.070
a fly stuck in my throat,

05:45.970 --> 05:47.770
forcing me to endure your acting

05:48.430 --> 05:49.390
and your lies.

05:49.490 --> 05:51.210
Enough, Xu Miyu.

05:51.600 --> 05:53.530
Is living with me that unbearable?

05:54.130 --> 05:54.890
Yes.

05:56.510 --> 05:57.120
Fine.

05:58.220 --> 05:59.280
You want a divorce?

05:59.790 --> 06:00.750
I agree!

06:24.190 --> 06:26.040
As for the family property,

06:26.680 --> 06:28.280
you get the house and the car.

06:28.280 --> 06:29.880
We split the savings in half.

06:30.000 --> 06:31.000
Do you agree?

06:32.240 --> 06:35.370
The house was bought
by my parents before we got married,

06:36.000 --> 06:37.930
so it definitely goes back to them.

06:38.390 --> 06:40.390
The car was bought after we got married,

06:40.390 --> 06:42.000
but you don't know how to drive.

06:42.000 --> 06:43.040
If we sell it,

06:43.040 --> 06:44.300
it won't be worth much.

06:44.600 --> 06:45.830
So the car belongs to me.

06:45.830 --> 06:46.610
Of course,

06:46.630 --> 06:48.560
you can use it if you need to.

06:49.070 --> 06:50.480
As for the savings,

06:51.680 --> 06:53.480
you manage all the money at home.

06:53.950 --> 06:54.950
You have my salary card.

06:54.950 --> 06:56.000
I'm not talking about your salary.

06:56.000 --> 06:56.720
I mean savings.

06:56.720 --> 06:58.070
I don't have any savings.

06:58.070 --> 07:00.000
You have my salary card.

07:01.040 --> 07:03.240
You manage all the living expenses.

07:03.240 --> 07:04.510
You know it best.

07:04.510 --> 07:07.270
The monthly utility bills,
living expenses,

07:07.750 --> 07:09.390
traveling a few times a year,

07:09.600 --> 07:11.600
and various subsidies for your family:

07:11.600 --> 07:14.160
your parents, your sister,
and your brother-in-law.

07:14.160 --> 07:17.070
-And travel...
-What about the 150,000 Minghui borrowed?

07:17.070 --> 07:19.270
That should be considered our savings.

07:19.600 --> 07:21.120
Half of it should be mine.

07:22.110 --> 07:23.570
You know about that money.

07:23.600 --> 07:24.600
It was given to the hospital,

07:24.600 --> 07:25.870
and it's impossible to get it back.

07:25.870 --> 07:27.470
I don't have any extra money.

07:27.800 --> 07:28.660
How about this?

07:29.430 --> 07:31.070
When I have a bit more money,

07:31.070 --> 07:33.240
I will transfer your half of the 75,000

07:33.510 --> 07:35.040
to you in installments.

07:37.510 --> 07:38.040
Nie Yucheng,

07:38.040 --> 07:39.680
you're really broke.

07:39.870 --> 07:42.680
It seems I really drained you
over these 10 years.

07:43.840 --> 07:44.930
Then what is this?

07:54.380 --> 07:55.330
[Project Investment Certificate]

07:55.330 --> 07:56.110
[Investor Information;
Investor Name: Nie Yucheng]

07:56.130 --> 07:57.240
[Project information; Project name:
Blue-chip Stock Investment]

07:57.260 --> 07:58.880
[Source of Funds]
[Breakdown of Fund Usage]

07:58.940 --> 08:00.800
This money is for my investments.

08:01.240 --> 08:02.230
I originally thought that if

08:02.230 --> 08:03.750
we were to have a child,

08:03.800 --> 08:05.720
we could buy a house
in a good school district.

08:05.720 --> 08:06.600
I'm sorry

08:06.950 --> 08:08.070
for letting you down.

08:08.070 --> 08:09.500
I'm telling the truth.

08:09.600 --> 08:11.040
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

08:11.040 --> 08:13.520
I was thinking that when
this investment matures

08:13.520 --> 08:14.600
and makes money,

08:15.840 --> 08:16.770
I'd give you a surprise.

08:16.770 --> 08:17.620
Okay.

08:18.280 --> 08:19.740
Then according to the terms,

08:19.740 --> 08:21.060
when it matures,

08:21.090 --> 08:23.890
we will split the principal
and interest equally.

08:24.510 --> 08:26.310
Sign here if there's no problem.

08:34.960 --> 08:35.630
Xu Miyu,

08:35.630 --> 08:38.390
you really impress me.

08:38.549 --> 08:40.750
You investigated me
behind my back, didn't you?

08:40.750 --> 08:42.179
For all these years,

08:43.000 --> 08:43.840
did you love me,

08:43.840 --> 08:45.000
or did you love my money?

08:45.000 --> 08:47.080
I should be the one asking that question.

08:47.080 --> 08:48.270
For all these years,

08:49.510 --> 08:50.960
did you love me,

08:51.000 --> 08:53.060
or did you love my selfless devotion?

08:53.480 --> 08:54.380
Wait, what do you mean?

08:54.380 --> 08:55.980
I mean that these 4 million

08:56.510 --> 08:57.610
might not be able to

08:57.960 --> 09:00.130
buy back my lost 10 years of youth,

09:00.240 --> 09:02.670
but at least it can save me some dignity

09:02.670 --> 09:03.600
and confidence.

09:06.310 --> 09:07.280
Sign it.

09:07.390 --> 09:08.790
What's the rush?

09:08.790 --> 09:10.120
Do you want to divorce me so badly?

09:10.120 --> 09:11.630
Do you hate me that much?

09:11.960 --> 09:13.390
Always talking about yourself...

09:13.390 --> 09:14.670
All you ever think about is yourself.

09:14.670 --> 09:16.670
You flatter yourself, Nie Yucheng.

09:16.710 --> 09:18.060
I'm not divorcing for you.

09:18.060 --> 09:19.390
I'm doing it for myself.

09:19.790 --> 09:20.670
I have wasted

09:20.670 --> 09:22.790
too much on you.

09:23.000 --> 09:25.930
I don't want to waste another second.

09:25.960 --> 09:27.080
Sign it.

09:35.960 --> 09:38.180
[Husband's fingerprint: Nie Yucheng]

09:38.630 --> 09:39.630
You're free.

09:41.270 --> 09:42.910
Enjoy your life.

09:43.630 --> 09:46.720
I'd like to see what you can achieve.

09:44.620 --> 09:45.440
[Husband's fingerprint: Nie Yucheng]

09:58.350 --> 09:59.400
Thank you.

10:05.270 --> 10:06.510
As we can see,

10:06.510 --> 10:08.200
there are some problems here.

10:09.510 --> 10:10.510
You have to think.

10:12.200 --> 10:12.960
You can go now.

10:12.960 --> 10:13.960
Of course.

10:17.390 --> 10:18.320
Are you alright?

10:19.200 --> 10:20.670
Landi Horse cheated us.

10:21.240 --> 10:22.390
Their chairman

10:22.390 --> 10:25.520
signed a contract
with the Future Group just yesterday.

10:25.740 --> 10:26.990
We are too late.

10:28.080 --> 10:29.510
You mean like yesterday?

10:29.510 --> 10:30.120
Yeah,

10:30.120 --> 10:31.200
just yesterday.

10:32.110 --> 10:33.200
I need to go find the chairman.

10:33.200 --> 10:33.790
Yes.

10:35.840 --> 10:37.820
I think it's too late to see him now.

10:38.120 --> 10:41.000
The chairman was on
a meditation retreat yesterday.

10:41.000 --> 10:43.660
There's no way he would
have taken any meetings.

10:44.370 --> 10:45.250
You know what?

10:45.520 --> 10:46.680
That news

10:46.790 --> 10:49.630
is probably just a bluff by Future Group.

11:09.040 --> 11:11.050
♪ Life is full of ♪

11:11.830 --> 11:14.520
♪ Countless crossroads ♪

11:13.070 --> 11:13.500
[Graduation Certificate]

11:13.500 --> 11:16.830
[General High School
Graduation Certificate]

11:16.190 --> 11:19.950
♪ Chase joy too hard, and it slips away ♪

11:20.460 --> 11:24.890
[Education background: Hushi University]

11:21.620 --> 11:23.570
♪ All those confusions ♪

11:24.220 --> 11:27.940
♪ No answers, no reasons ♪

11:28.820 --> 11:32.820
♪ Throwing ourselves
into the tide of the unknown ♪

11:31.100 --> 11:32.320
[Hotel environment]

11:32.420 --> 11:33.740
[Positions at Star Vault Hotel]

11:33.790 --> 11:34.490
[Enjoying unparalleled working benefits]

11:34.490 --> 11:36.200
[Travel bonus and benefits]
[Recognition and reward]

11:36.220 --> 11:38.630
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

11:36.360 --> 11:37.560
[Keep in touch]

11:39.750 --> 11:41.670
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

11:39.980 --> 11:41.190
[Xu Miyu] [Resume] [Upload Attachment]

11:41.940 --> 11:42.350
[Attachment Management]

11:42.440 --> 11:43.790
[Xu Miyu's personal resume]

11:43.150 --> 11:47.150
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

11:43.860 --> 11:44.180
[Open]

11:44.670 --> 11:45.740
[Resume]

11:45.740 --> 11:47.410
[Upload Attachment]

11:47.490 --> 11:48.170
[Xu Miyu]

11:48.190 --> 11:49.590
[Personal Strengths:
Positive and outgoing personality]

11:49.020 --> 11:50.950
♪ Busy and restless ♪

11:49.620 --> 11:51.320
[A strong sense of responsibility
and team spirit]

11:51.350 --> 11:52.430
[Desired Position: Full-time]

11:51.420 --> 11:54.850
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

11:52.460 --> 11:53.650
[Role experience] [Work experience]

11:53.680 --> 11:54.390
[Project experience]

11:54.410 --> 11:55.290
[Education: Hushi University,
Bachelor's in Hotel Management]

11:56.170 --> 12:00.340
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

12:02.260 --> 12:04.720
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

12:05.940 --> 12:07.910
♪ Don't look back ♪

12:08.940 --> 12:10.670
♪ I've already learned ♪

12:10.060 --> 12:12.980
[Seller: Ji Feng; Buyer: Nolan]

12:11.490 --> 12:15.200
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

12:13.270 --> 12:14.450
How did you do this?

12:14.880 --> 12:16.040
We finally made it.

12:16.010 --> 12:17.580
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

12:18.270 --> 12:18.690
[Seller: Ji Feng; Buyer: Nolan]

12:18.530 --> 12:22.450
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

12:18.990 --> 12:19.780
Kenny.

12:21.150 --> 12:22.340
First of all,

12:23.100 --> 12:25.410
my congrats to you
on signing this contract.

12:23.400 --> 12:26.140
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

12:25.520 --> 12:26.440
But

12:26.470 --> 12:29.670
vast majority of the effort
on signing this contract

12:27.030 --> 12:29.240
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

12:30.170 --> 12:31.540
was made by me

12:30.260 --> 12:31.740
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

12:32.220 --> 12:33.490
and my team.

12:33.510 --> 12:35.290
Keep your contract.

12:35.840 --> 12:36.780
What?

12:37.130 --> 12:38.210
And your hotel.

12:44.790 --> 12:47.200
♪ Knowing when to advance or retreat,
yet still asleep ♪

12:48.310 --> 12:49.500
♪ Rushing to ripen before our time ♪

12:51.720 --> 12:56.130
♪ Sighing at partings,
who meets whom at which crossing ♪

12:53.470 --> 12:55.420
Kenny, hope to see you soon.

12:55.650 --> 12:56.530
Goodbye.

12:57.590 --> 12:59.520
♪ Busy and restless ♪

12:59.990 --> 13:03.530
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

13:04.740 --> 13:08.910
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

13:10.830 --> 13:13.290
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

13:14.510 --> 13:16.480
♪ Don't look back ♪

13:17.510 --> 13:19.240
♪ I've already learned ♪

13:20.010 --> 13:23.910
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

13:24.580 --> 13:26.280
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

13:26.900 --> 13:30.900
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

13:31.970 --> 13:34.710
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

13:35.600 --> 13:37.860
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

13:38.760 --> 13:40.110
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

14:14.180 --> 14:15.050
Ms. Xu,

14:15.150 --> 14:17.420
Room 1819 is ready for you.

14:17.480 --> 14:18.380
[Purong Hotel]

14:18.510 --> 14:19.910
I don't want 1819.

14:19.940 --> 14:21.200
Please change my room.

14:22.120 --> 14:22.710
Okay.

14:26.900 --> 14:27.830
Enjoy your stay.

14:28.320 --> 14:28.970
Thank you.

14:32.840 --> 14:34.260
Good evening, ma'am.

14:35.300 --> 14:36.300
This way, please.

14:43.030 --> 14:44.150
Welcome.

14:48.560 --> 14:49.570
Please come in.

14:57.080 --> 14:57.960
I'd like to order.

14:57.960 --> 14:59.030
Certainly, ma'am.

14:59.030 --> 15:00.030
To order, please dial...

15:00.030 --> 15:01.290
I want Boston lobster.

15:03.150 --> 15:03.910
Boston lobster.

15:03.910 --> 15:05.870
And bluefin tuna,

15:05.870 --> 15:07.200
stir-fried sea snails,

15:07.670 --> 15:09.200
and wine-marinated crab.

15:09.220 --> 15:10.980
For one person,

15:11.030 --> 15:12.030
this might be a bit too much.

15:12.030 --> 15:13.080
It's been exactly 10 years

15:13.080 --> 15:14.150
since I last had a proper seafood meal.

15:14.150 --> 15:16.030
I'm going to eat to
my heart's content today.

15:16.030 --> 15:17.890
And give me a serving of ark shell.

15:20.250 --> 15:21.300
What's going on?

15:21.750 --> 15:22.270
Never mind.

15:22.270 --> 15:24.000
Haven't we seen enough of this?

15:24.030 --> 15:24.670
F&B Department.

15:24.670 --> 15:27.070
A guest on the executive floor
is ordering.

15:45.300 --> 15:47.230
I used to think

15:47.730 --> 15:49.030
that giving all of myself

15:49.030 --> 15:50.600
to another person

15:50.600 --> 15:52.750
was also a form of self-realization.

15:53.910 --> 15:55.480
Until one day I came to my senses

15:55.480 --> 15:56.600
and realized

15:57.030 --> 15:59.860
that I had been
treating myself so carelessly,

16:00.040 --> 16:02.040
losing myself further and further.

16:02.160 --> 16:04.280
Forget about the stomach-soothing meal.

16:04.280 --> 16:06.270
Let your mistress make it for you.

16:10.000 --> 16:12.120
But now I'm going to pick myself up.

16:12.720 --> 16:13.690
Stop ordering her around,

16:13.690 --> 16:14.790
stop criticizing her,

16:14.790 --> 16:16.650
and let her do whatever she wants.

16:17.360 --> 16:19.220
I hope she can live

16:19.870 --> 16:22.240
every day for her own happiness.

16:23.510 --> 16:24.600
Xu Miyu,

16:26.520 --> 16:27.610
good job.

16:28.210 --> 16:30.430
♪ That fleeting moment I tried to hold ♪

16:31.220 --> 16:33.890
♪ Let it go when the glass runs dry ♪

16:35.280 --> 16:38.190
♪ Unfinished longings ♪

16:38.880 --> 16:42.010
♪ Drift like fading embers ♪

16:43.170 --> 16:45.290
♪ Still longing for yesterday's glow ♪

16:46.140 --> 16:49.100
♪ Yet sailing into
the ocean's depths at night ♪

16:50.130 --> 16:53.150
♪ Questions without answers ♪

16:54.080 --> 16:56.860
♪ Let them go with the wind ♪

16:58.050 --> 16:59.820
♪ Let them go ♪

17:53.610 --> 17:54.360
Hello?

17:55.220 --> 17:56.600
Clean the room,

17:57.030 --> 17:57.840
now.

18:02.790 --> 18:03.220
Hello,

18:03.250 --> 18:04.530
room service.

19:56.570 --> 19:57.580
[October 31]

20:06.990 --> 20:07.250
[Message]

20:07.250 --> 20:08.850
[Ms. Xu Miyu, we regret to
inform you that your profile

20:08.870 --> 20:10.910
[is not the best fit for this role.]

20:22.170 --> 20:22.590
[Hello, I'm very interested
in the Housekeeping Supervisor position]

20:22.590 --> 20:23.020
[(5-day workweek with 2 days off)...]

20:23.160 --> 20:24.460
[JD Cleaning Specialist — 8,000 RMB/month]

20:24.480 --> 20:26.030
[Free training, stable orders]

20:26.230 --> 20:26.790
[JD Hiring Cleaning Specialists Urgently;
8,000 RMB/month]

20:26.820 --> 20:27.480
[Jobs assigned nearby, steady orders]

20:30.590 --> 20:32.020
[Competition Analysis]

20:34.230 --> 20:36.300
[Manting Art Hotel]

20:36.600 --> 20:39.880
[Update on Your Application for
the Assistant General Manager Position]

20:39.160 --> 20:40.240
Hello.

20:40.240 --> 20:41.440
I interviewed

20:41.440 --> 20:42.750
at your hotel recently.

20:42.750 --> 20:44.400
My name is Xu Miyu.

20:44.670 --> 20:46.730
I just received the rejection letter.

20:46.730 --> 20:47.960
I would like

20:48.030 --> 20:49.590
to explain a few things.

20:49.590 --> 20:50.880
Could you give me another chance?

20:50.880 --> 20:52.070
I am sorry, ma'am.

20:52.070 --> 20:54.000
The employee we hired
has already started today.

20:54.000 --> 20:55.640
Please try other companies.

20:55.640 --> 20:56.240
Goodbye.

21:04.270 --> 21:04.510
Hello.

21:04.510 --> 21:05.640
Mr. Su.

21:06.750 --> 21:07.590
What?

21:09.230 --> 21:10.710
The 8 million is gone?

21:10.740 --> 21:13.870
The opposing lawyer
sent me an investment report today.

21:14.630 --> 21:16.560
This project is currently
suffering severe losses.

21:16.560 --> 21:17.540
Not only is there no profit,

21:17.540 --> 21:19.160
but there is also a debt
of over 2 million.

21:19.160 --> 21:20.440
Mr. Nie stated

21:20.460 --> 21:22.550
that he doesn't plan
to split the debt with you.

21:22.550 --> 21:23.790
He will bear it himself

21:23.790 --> 21:25.590
and wants to negotiate with you.

21:26.070 --> 21:27.890
This is definitely Nie Yucheng's trick.

21:27.890 --> 21:29.660
He just wants to stall and not pay.

21:29.660 --> 21:31.600
But his trick worked.

21:31.920 --> 21:32.790
Why?

21:32.790 --> 21:34.550
Because this amount was in the negative

21:34.550 --> 21:35.960
during your marriage.

21:35.960 --> 21:38.030
Even if it turns into a profit later,

21:38.030 --> 21:39.440
according to the Marriage Law,

21:39.440 --> 21:41.310
since your marriage is already dissolved,

21:41.310 --> 21:42.680
it will no longer be considered

21:42.680 --> 21:44.280
your joint property.

21:44.510 --> 21:45.680
Which means

21:46.400 --> 21:47.550
he no longer has to split it with you.

21:47.550 --> 21:48.750
Knowing Nie Yucheng,

21:48.750 --> 21:51.310
he'd never make such a losing investment.

21:52.310 --> 21:54.640
He's obviously transferring his assets.

21:54.830 --> 21:56.440
Can I sue him?

21:56.440 --> 21:57.550
It will take time.

21:58.200 --> 21:59.930
We don't have enough evidence.

22:00.270 --> 22:02.360
Now is not the best time to sue.

22:02.440 --> 22:04.070
I'm not completely sure we can win.

22:04.070 --> 22:05.400
I can find the evidence.

22:05.730 --> 22:07.040
And I can wait.

22:08.200 --> 22:09.550
I must get this money.

22:10.400 --> 22:12.400
Mr. Su, you have to help me.

22:18.640 --> 22:19.570
Good morning, ma'am.

22:19.570 --> 22:20.640
Hello. I'd like to check out.

22:20.640 --> 22:21.270
Okay.

22:24.400 --> 22:25.440
Did you rest well last night,

22:25.440 --> 22:26.400
Ms. Xu?

22:27.030 --> 22:27.790
It was fine.

22:28.160 --> 22:29.270
Your total comes

22:29.270 --> 22:30.920
to 6,680 yuan.

22:30.920 --> 22:33.030
Would you like to pay by phone or card?

22:33.030 --> 22:34.680
6,680?

22:35.310 --> 22:37.920
Isn't your executive suite only 2,300?

22:37.920 --> 22:38.790
The alcohol in the room

22:38.790 --> 22:41.070
and the meals you ordered
are charged separately.

22:41.070 --> 22:41.830
You ordered

22:41.830 --> 22:43.750
2,190 yuan worth of seafood

22:43.750 --> 22:45.350
and 540 yuan worth of drinks,

22:45.510 --> 22:47.640
plus a 100 yuan room service fee.

22:48.960 --> 22:50.270
Here is your itemized bill.

22:50.270 --> 22:52.750
Then what's the other 1,550 for?

22:52.750 --> 22:54.550
You ruined 2 of our carpets

22:54.550 --> 22:56.200
and a crystal ornament.

22:56.200 --> 22:57.510
So...

22:57.510 --> 22:58.550
I'm sorry.

22:58.750 --> 22:59.680
I forgot.

22:59.710 --> 23:00.640
Ms. Xu.

23:00.640 --> 23:02.790
So, will you pay by phone or card?

23:02.790 --> 23:03.640
WeChat Pay.

23:10.290 --> 23:11.050
Thank you.

23:15.780 --> 23:17.140
Welcome.

23:18.630 --> 23:19.300
I'm sorry.

23:19.320 --> 23:20.040
It's okay.

23:28.790 --> 23:30.280
Thank you for staying with us.

23:29.400 --> 23:32.370
[14 years ago]

23:32.460 --> 23:33.460
[Purong Hotel]

23:33.550 --> 23:34.480
Hello.

23:34.020 --> 23:37.330
[Young Ji Feng]

23:34.480 --> 23:36.070
I'm the new intern starting today.

23:36.070 --> 23:37.550
Where should I report?

23:37.550 --> 23:38.510
Take the staff entrance.

23:38.510 --> 23:39.410
It's right over there.

23:39.410 --> 23:40.440
Okay, thank you.

23:41.100 --> 23:42.030
Welcome aboard,

23:42.030 --> 23:42.890
new colleague.

23:53.720 --> 23:55.250
The elevator is over there.

23:56.790 --> 23:57.960
Hello.

23:58.630 --> 24:00.210
Eighth floor?

24:04.420 --> 24:05.230
Check-in.

24:06.000 --> 24:06.720
Hello, sir.

24:06.720 --> 24:07.510
Welcome.

24:09.030 --> 24:09.960
Mr. Ji.

24:11.790 --> 24:14.310
I see you booked our executive floor.

24:14.590 --> 24:16.480
Would you like to check in early?

24:16.480 --> 24:17.270
Yes.

24:18.310 --> 24:20.840
Then I suggest you
sign up for our membership.

24:21.460 --> 24:21.940
[Join as a VIP for RMB 50,000]

24:21.960 --> 24:22.520
[and enjoy exclusive privileges]

24:22.750 --> 24:25.030
With a membership, you can check in early

24:25.030 --> 24:26.350
and enjoy a 20% discount

24:26.350 --> 24:28.610
at the Western and Chinese restaurants.

24:28.790 --> 24:29.550
No, thanks.

24:29.750 --> 24:31.110
I just want to check in early.

24:31.110 --> 24:32.910
You want me to spend 50,000 yuan?

24:35.310 --> 24:36.310
Check-in for non-members

24:36.310 --> 24:37.960
starts at 2 PM.

24:38.270 --> 24:40.470
I suggest you come back this afternoon.

24:42.910 --> 24:43.210
[Black Card VIP at Purong Hotel]

24:44.960 --> 24:46.090
With this,

24:46.110 --> 24:47.460
can I check in early?

24:49.040 --> 24:50.170
Yes, sir.

24:50.190 --> 24:51.650
I'll handle it for you now.

25:05.720 --> 25:06.890
Hello.

25:08.590 --> 25:09.200
Okay.

25:09.200 --> 25:10.660
I'll send it up right away.

25:11.270 --> 25:11.960
Okay.

25:16.070 --> 25:16.830
It's done.

25:17.030 --> 25:17.720
Thank you.

25:18.640 --> 25:19.480
Thanks.

25:22.720 --> 25:23.610
Cover for me.

25:23.640 --> 25:24.480
Mr. Ji.

25:25.270 --> 25:26.030
Mr. Ji.

25:26.830 --> 25:27.430
Excuse me.

25:27.880 --> 25:28.480
What is it?

25:28.480 --> 25:30.810
You are a Black Card VIP
guest of our hotel.

25:30.830 --> 25:32.070
The system just showed

25:32.070 --> 25:33.550
that you will be staying here
for a long time.

25:33.550 --> 25:34.720
If you don't mind,

25:34.720 --> 25:36.200
I can show you around

25:36.200 --> 25:37.070
to get familiar with the place.

25:37.070 --> 25:38.270
Would you like that?

25:38.820 --> 25:39.580
Sure.

25:40.140 --> 25:41.140
This way, please.

25:42.200 --> 25:43.440
Our Purong Hotel

25:43.440 --> 25:45.920
has been established
for nearly half a century.

25:45.920 --> 25:46.720
In Shanghai,

25:46.720 --> 25:49.480
it is a well-known,
established 5-star hotel.

25:50.880 --> 25:51.790
On your right-hand side

25:51.790 --> 25:53.720
is our hotel's banquet hall.

25:53.790 --> 25:55.240
It has hosted

25:55.240 --> 25:56.930
a wide variety of business banquets.

25:56.930 --> 25:58.700
[Young Ji Feng]

25:57.070 --> 25:58.790
It can accommodate

25:58.790 --> 26:00.000
around 200 people.

26:00.110 --> 26:02.030
If you need it in the future,

26:02.030 --> 26:02.790
you can always

26:02.790 --> 26:05.450
contact our front office
to make a reservation.

26:06.110 --> 26:08.000
Over the years, our Purong Hotel

26:08.000 --> 26:09.830
has kept pace with the times.

26:10.030 --> 26:13.110
Both in terms of decor and cuisine,

26:13.110 --> 26:15.510
it combines Chinese and Western elements.

26:16.110 --> 26:17.030
As for the dishes,

26:17.030 --> 26:18.310
we have a variety of flavors.

26:18.310 --> 26:21.270
You can choose
according to your preference.

26:21.550 --> 26:22.750
If you need to,

26:22.750 --> 26:24.790
you can also contact us
for a reservation anytime.

26:24.790 --> 26:26.720
Here is our Western restaurant,

26:26.720 --> 26:28.000
where you can

26:28.000 --> 26:30.590
taste delicacies from all over the world.

26:30.720 --> 26:33.110
Our newly introduced
afternoon tea and desserts

26:33.110 --> 26:35.350
are extremely delicious.

26:35.350 --> 26:36.160
If you have time,

26:36.160 --> 26:37.760
you should come and try them.

26:45.240 --> 26:46.720
What is that smell?

26:47.610 --> 26:48.610
What?

26:50.430 --> 26:51.390
I feel like

26:51.440 --> 26:52.860
there's a very pungent smell here.

26:52.860 --> 26:53.920
Don't you smell it?

26:54.600 --> 26:56.350
It should be the smell of disinfectant.

26:56.350 --> 26:57.830
This smell is expected

26:57.830 --> 26:59.290
during routine cleaning.

27:00.110 --> 27:01.110
This way, please.

27:04.830 --> 27:05.790
Mr. Ji,

27:05.810 --> 27:08.000
this is our executive lounge.

27:08.000 --> 27:09.590
It is an exclusive space designed

27:09.590 --> 27:11.510
for our VIP guests on the executive floor,

27:11.510 --> 27:14.000
providing exquisite dining

27:14.000 --> 27:16.460
and personalized service around the clock.

27:22.880 --> 27:24.200
If you're interested later,

27:24.200 --> 27:25.930
you can come and experience it.

27:58.590 --> 27:59.550
So,

27:59.880 --> 28:02.590
Mr. Ji, are you satisfied with the tour?

28:03.890 --> 28:05.090
I'm curious

28:05.120 --> 28:06.000
how Purong Hotel

28:06.000 --> 28:07.310
keeps its guests now.

28:08.550 --> 28:09.510
I'm sorry?

28:11.200 --> 28:13.110
Your front desk staff is slack,

28:13.400 --> 28:15.240
and the hallways smell like disinfectant.

28:15.240 --> 28:16.640
After this tour you gave me,

28:16.640 --> 28:18.170
do you think I'm satisfied?

28:22.280 --> 28:23.200
Mr. Ji.

28:23.230 --> 28:24.030
I...

28:24.050 --> 28:25.380
That's not what I meant.

28:27.160 --> 28:27.960
Mr. Ji,

28:28.310 --> 28:30.740
you're our distinguished Black Card VIP.

28:30.790 --> 28:32.030
I'm your butler, Yin Xiang.

28:32.030 --> 28:33.830
Feel free to contact me
if you need anything.

28:33.830 --> 28:35.830
-Okay. Thank you.
-Enjoy your stay.

28:39.350 --> 28:39.720
Well.

28:39.720 --> 28:40.550
Let's go.

28:40.550 --> 28:41.880
Is he crazy?

28:43.640 --> 28:45.310
We have a difficult Black Card VIP.

28:45.310 --> 28:46.270
His surname is Ji.

28:46.270 --> 28:47.530
Everyone, be careful.

29:19.200 --> 29:21.720
This is your future service standard

29:22.310 --> 29:24.640
and the service attitude you must uphold.

29:25.880 --> 29:28.480
Today is your first day on the job.

29:28.550 --> 29:31.480
I want you to listen carefully

29:31.480 --> 29:33.310
to what I have to say next.

29:33.830 --> 29:35.830
In the future, no matter

29:35.830 --> 29:38.350
which position you rotate to in the hotel,

29:38.350 --> 29:39.880
you must firmly remember:

29:40.030 --> 29:41.400
Making guests feel at home

29:41.400 --> 29:44.110
is the service tenet of our Purong Hotel.

29:44.310 --> 29:47.380
It might sound a bit cliché,

29:47.590 --> 29:49.030
but I believe

29:49.030 --> 29:51.950
it's the foundation of our hotel service.

29:52.110 --> 29:54.160
When a guest walks into the hotel,

29:54.270 --> 29:56.670
every part of our hotel

29:56.690 --> 29:58.780
starts working for them.

29:58.810 --> 30:01.000
We need to keenly perceive

30:01.020 --> 30:03.020
every need of the guest

30:03.050 --> 30:05.900
and cater to all their senses,

30:06.350 --> 30:10.160
providing service
more caring than being at home.

30:10.180 --> 30:12.260
Purong Hotel was established

30:12.350 --> 30:13.810
nearly half a century ago,

30:13.880 --> 30:16.640
and this is how we retain our guests.

30:17.460 --> 30:19.400
In your future work,

30:19.430 --> 30:20.630
I hope

30:20.680 --> 30:23.110
in every service,

30:23.130 --> 30:24.370
you can understand

30:24.400 --> 30:26.800
the meaning of working in a hotel.

30:26.820 --> 30:28.340
This is also the value

30:28.370 --> 30:30.170
that Purong provides you.

31:28.140 --> 31:31.490
[Hotel Manager] [Details]

31:31.590 --> 31:32.380
[Requirements: At least 5 years of
experience in hotel management]

31:32.400 --> 31:33.490
[and operations. Base salary:
8,000 RMB + commission]

31:39.430 --> 31:40.600
[Compensation & Benefitst]

31:40.600 --> 31:42.520
[Salary Expectation (Monthly, RMB)]

31:44.160 --> 31:45.510
[Salary Expectation (Monthly, RMB)]

31:45.540 --> 31:47.680
[Compensation & Benefitst]

31:55.110 --> 31:55.750
Come.

31:55.770 --> 31:57.780
Here. Be careful.

32:02.230 --> 32:02.920
Okay.

32:03.890 --> 32:04.820
Come.

32:06.730 --> 32:08.530
The room might not be big,

32:08.560 --> 32:09.920
but the location is great.

32:09.920 --> 32:11.500
Transport is convenient.

32:11.530 --> 32:13.640
You step right out into the downtown area.

32:13.640 --> 32:16.400
And look, your bed is up here.

32:16.510 --> 32:17.830
It's very private.

32:17.830 --> 32:19.110
4,000 yuan a month.

32:19.110 --> 32:20.370
It's really a bargain.

32:22.130 --> 32:24.600
Can you make it a bit cheaper?

32:28.380 --> 32:29.290
How about this?

32:29.640 --> 32:31.590
If you can

32:31.650 --> 32:33.570
pay 6 months' rent at once,

32:33.880 --> 32:36.000
I'll let you have it for 3,500 a month.

32:36.030 --> 32:37.710
That saves you 3,000 in total.

32:37.730 --> 32:38.430
Okay.

32:38.450 --> 32:39.340
Deal.

32:39.370 --> 32:39.910
Great.

32:41.080 --> 32:42.160
Here, scan my code.

32:43.260 --> 32:43.480
[Loading]

32:46.150 --> 32:47.740
[Payment to Individual: RMB 21,000]

32:50.350 --> 32:51.240
All right.

32:51.680 --> 32:53.200
Keep this key.

32:53.750 --> 32:54.480
And you can

32:54.480 --> 32:55.400
tidy up by yourself.

32:55.400 --> 32:56.640
I'll get going now.

32:57.110 --> 32:57.480
Alright.

32:57.480 --> 32:58.350
Thank you.

32:58.350 --> 32:59.070
Bye.

33:03.430 --> 33:04.610
[My balance: 1,407 yuan]

33:12.360 --> 33:13.550
Hello.

33:16.440 --> 33:17.030
Yes, it's me.

33:17.030 --> 33:18.360
I submitted the resume.

33:19.590 --> 33:20.590
Okay.

33:20.590 --> 33:21.790
I'll be right there.

33:24.410 --> 33:30.640
[Xiaoma Hotel]

33:26.890 --> 33:27.440
I remember

33:27.440 --> 33:28.310
your resume.

33:29.310 --> 33:31.100
After being a housewife for 10 years,

33:31.100 --> 33:33.660
do you think you are up to this job?

33:33.690 --> 33:35.020
Well, ma'am,

33:35.090 --> 33:37.440
although I don't have
much work experience,

33:37.440 --> 33:38.830
I graduated from Hushi University

33:38.830 --> 33:40.690
with a major in hotel management.

33:40.720 --> 33:43.030
When it comes to
handling practical matters,

33:43.030 --> 33:44.420
I also have some experience.

33:44.420 --> 33:46.680
For instance, I handle
our family's utility bills

33:46.680 --> 33:48.830
and commercial insurance contracts...

33:48.830 --> 33:50.270
We are a hotel.

33:50.300 --> 33:52.740
Do you understand
the current hotel business?

33:52.740 --> 33:53.740
My husband...

33:56.370 --> 33:58.770
I've stayed in many hotels
in recent years.

33:59.080 --> 34:01.120
And regarding hotel management knowledge,

34:01.120 --> 34:02.130
I haven't let it slip either.

34:02.130 --> 34:03.180
What kind of hotels have you stayed in?

34:03.180 --> 34:04.130
Many.

34:04.160 --> 34:06.000
Like Aman in Japan

34:06.020 --> 34:08.139
and Banyan Tree in Morocco.

34:08.440 --> 34:09.770
Also...

34:09.860 --> 34:11.139
[Xiaoma Hotel]

34:13.030 --> 34:14.400
Hampton by Hilton

34:14.429 --> 34:15.960
and Fairfield by Marriott.

34:16.030 --> 34:16.920
Even budget hotels

34:16.920 --> 34:18.070
like Home Inn and Hanting,

34:18.070 --> 34:19.400
I've stayed in them too.

34:22.409 --> 34:23.679
I know your concerns.

34:24.190 --> 34:25.590
In terms of work experience,

34:25.590 --> 34:27.070
I am indeed lacking.

34:27.090 --> 34:29.290
So I am willing to start from the basics

34:29.310 --> 34:30.580
and I will work hard to catch up.

34:30.580 --> 34:31.850
Here,

34:32.150 --> 34:33.440
we actually value

34:33.440 --> 34:35.040
practical business skills.

34:35.120 --> 34:36.400
If we let you start right away,

34:36.400 --> 34:37.400
can you handle it?

34:37.560 --> 34:38.389
I can.

34:38.449 --> 34:39.590
[Xiaoma Hotel]

34:39.760 --> 34:40.949
Welcome to the team.

34:44.230 --> 34:45.880
Am I hired just like that?

34:46.030 --> 34:47.739
What about the salary and benefits?

34:47.739 --> 34:48.889
The position you interviewed for

34:48.889 --> 34:50.070
has already been filled.

34:50.070 --> 34:50.760
However,

34:50.780 --> 34:52.960
we can transfer you to a sales position.

34:52.960 --> 34:54.929
This position is commission-based.

34:54.929 --> 34:57.610
The base salary is 3,500 yuan a month.

34:57.860 --> 34:59.320
Is that acceptable to you?

35:00.020 --> 35:00.860
I see.

35:01.070 --> 35:02.070
Ms. Xu,

35:02.070 --> 35:03.960
your competitive advantage is not obvious,

35:03.960 --> 35:06.400
and you have a 10-year
gap in your work experience.

35:06.400 --> 35:07.690
Given your current qualifications,

35:07.690 --> 35:10.420
this is the best offer we can make.

35:09.350 --> 35:11.760
[Xiaoma Hotel Labor Contract]

35:21.560 --> 35:23.800
Can I get a 2-month advance on my salary?

35:23.820 --> 35:26.260
You can't get an advance during probation.

35:26.910 --> 35:28.660
I'm really in a tight spot.

35:28.790 --> 35:29.790
Tell you what,

35:29.810 --> 35:31.510
we happen to have a client today.

35:31.510 --> 35:32.760
If you go and win him over,

35:32.760 --> 35:34.510
the bonus is 5,000.

35:34.550 --> 35:35.680
How do I win him over?

35:36.090 --> 35:37.260
Ms. Xu,

35:37.670 --> 35:40.130
you have to figure out
how to work on your own.

35:42.300 --> 35:44.900
Then please send me
the client's information.

35:44.940 --> 35:45.750
Okay.

35:58.030 --> 35:58.880
Hello?

35:58.900 --> 36:00.700
Mr. Mai, I've arrived.

36:02.810 --> 36:04.130
Where are you?

36:05.670 --> 36:06.800
I... I can't hear you.

36:06.800 --> 36:07.510
What did you say?

36:07.510 --> 36:08.840
Hello?

36:13.300 --> 36:14.430
You wanted to see me?

36:14.730 --> 36:15.520
Qiaoqi.

36:15.540 --> 36:16.590
We've only been dating for a month.

36:16.590 --> 36:18.070
You can't just break up with me like that.

36:18.070 --> 36:20.000
If I did something wrong,

36:20.020 --> 36:21.610
-Tell me. I can...
-Stop. Stop.

36:21.610 --> 36:22.880
I'll make it short.

36:23.010 --> 36:24.590
I don't do long-term relationships.

36:24.590 --> 36:26.170
Getting back together
is absolutely impossible.

36:26.170 --> 36:27.150
If you really need
something in the future,

36:27.150 --> 36:28.570
you're always welcome to find me.

36:28.570 --> 36:30.260
But if you try to harass me,

36:30.290 --> 36:31.820
I'll pull all your hair out.

36:36.580 --> 36:38.520
Hello? What?

36:38.550 --> 36:40.070
Over here.

36:40.490 --> 36:41.480
Mr. Mai.

36:41.500 --> 36:43.400
-I'm with Xiaoma Hotel...
-I've been waiting for you.

36:43.400 --> 36:45.230
Have a seat.

36:45.500 --> 36:46.600
Ms. Xu.

36:47.210 --> 36:49.760
Actually, you can make money

36:49.840 --> 36:51.760
off me so easily.

36:52.640 --> 36:55.050
Finish this drink, and I'll sign.

36:55.210 --> 36:57.170
Finish it.

36:57.190 --> 36:58.730
Finish it.

36:59.400 --> 37:00.230
Finish it.

37:01.250 --> 37:02.040
Okay.

37:03.760 --> 37:06.140
Great!

37:06.170 --> 37:08.180
Good drinker.

37:08.410 --> 37:09.330
Impressive.

37:09.360 --> 37:11.920
You can really hold your liquor, Ms. Xu.

37:11.920 --> 37:13.230
Great.

37:13.430 --> 37:14.690
Ms. Xu, please...

37:16.540 --> 37:18.540
We all came out to have fun.

37:18.560 --> 37:20.210
No need to be so shy.

37:20.240 --> 37:22.210
I'm actually very gentle.

37:24.740 --> 37:25.770
You're unbelievable!

37:25.770 --> 37:27.080
How dare you push me!

37:27.560 --> 37:29.680
Didn't your mother
ever tell you not to hit women?

37:29.680 --> 37:30.760
What are you standing around for?

37:30.760 --> 37:31.510
Get them!

37:32.880 --> 37:33.710
Let's go.

37:34.010 --> 37:35.470
Darn it!

37:45.310 --> 37:46.880
What's going on with you, Xu Miyu?

37:46.880 --> 37:47.770
Instead of staying at home,

37:47.770 --> 37:48.900
you came here to drink with clients?

37:48.900 --> 37:50.360
Do you think this is a game?

37:51.880 --> 37:52.920
I got divorced.

37:53.180 --> 37:54.140
What did you say?

37:56.320 --> 37:57.150
Wait.

37:57.170 --> 37:58.360
What exactly happened?

37:58.360 --> 37:59.240
I got divorced.

38:00.960 --> 38:02.360
I have nothing left.

38:21.410 --> 38:22.330
Then...

38:22.890 --> 38:24.220
About your divorce,

38:24.250 --> 38:25.560
do your parents know?

38:26.570 --> 38:28.090
I wouldn't dare tell them.

38:28.600 --> 38:29.880
In their eyes,

38:29.880 --> 38:31.810
I finally found a good man to marry,

38:31.870 --> 38:33.730
so they can stop worrying about me

38:33.920 --> 38:35.370
and enjoy a good life.

38:35.390 --> 38:37.900
If I tell them I'm divorced now

38:38.070 --> 38:39.730
and still haven't found a job,

38:40.340 --> 38:42.870
how can they hold
their heads high in the town?

38:44.290 --> 38:45.520
Xu Miyu.

38:45.550 --> 38:46.760
You know what I've hated most about you

38:46.760 --> 38:48.190
since we were kids?

38:48.340 --> 38:50.330
You only care about what others think

38:50.330 --> 38:52.130
and never think about yourself.

38:53.290 --> 38:54.790
You finally have your freedom now.

38:54.790 --> 38:57.050
Can you please care more about yourself?

39:03.280 --> 39:04.080
You're right.

39:04.650 --> 39:05.670
That's what I was thinking too.

39:05.670 --> 39:06.710
So lately,

39:06.740 --> 39:09.450
I've been trying hard to find a hotel job.

39:10.090 --> 39:11.190
I want to

39:11.730 --> 39:12.800
go back to 10 years ago,

39:12.800 --> 39:14.550
to the turning point that changed my life,

39:14.550 --> 39:16.480
and see if, through my own efforts,

39:16.710 --> 39:18.480
I can realize my own value.

39:18.480 --> 39:20.000
That's the spirit.

39:20.970 --> 39:22.880
But if you want a hotel job,

39:22.880 --> 39:24.360
why didn't you tell me?

39:24.360 --> 39:25.480
Didn't I tell you last time

39:25.480 --> 39:27.010
that I work at Purong Hotel?

39:27.230 --> 39:29.400
Why would Purong Hotel hire me?

39:29.420 --> 39:30.660
I'm not qualified.

39:30.690 --> 39:33.120
A famous 5-star hotel in Shanghai.

39:33.150 --> 39:34.970
I can't even reach it on my tiptoes.

39:34.970 --> 39:35.760
If you can't reach it,

39:35.760 --> 39:37.460
why don't you get a ladder?

39:37.480 --> 39:38.920
I am your ladder.

39:41.110 --> 39:42.150
It's just that

39:42.260 --> 39:44.720
your ex-husband
is in the tourism industry.

39:44.760 --> 39:46.840
He'll inevitably deal with Purong.

39:47.070 --> 39:49.310
If you really join Purong,

39:49.760 --> 39:50.440
and in case

39:50.440 --> 39:52.400
you guys run into each other,

39:52.800 --> 39:54.110
you need to be mentally prepared.

39:54.110 --> 39:55.050
I don't care.

39:55.630 --> 39:57.960
I just want to do
what I want to do right now.

39:59.200 --> 40:01.110
I'm relieved to hear that.

40:04.070 --> 40:05.510
Our hotel's marketing department

40:05.510 --> 40:06.900
has an interview tomorrow.

40:06.900 --> 40:08.360
I've referred you.

40:08.630 --> 40:09.960
Someone will add you on WeChat later.

40:09.960 --> 40:11.220
Remember to accept it.

40:11.480 --> 40:13.170
Thank you, Qiaoqi.

40:13.940 --> 40:15.310
I will definitely work hard.

40:15.310 --> 40:16.830
It's just a small favor.

40:16.850 --> 40:18.580
I can't just shove you in there.

40:18.580 --> 40:19.880
I already feel like

40:19.880 --> 40:21.830
I'm getting something for nothing.

40:21.830 --> 40:23.910
You didn't get something for nothing.

40:23.910 --> 40:25.850
You just lost too much.

40:27.210 --> 40:29.340
Good thing you cut your losses in time.

40:29.630 --> 40:30.360
From now on,

40:30.840 --> 40:32.100
it'll all be good days.

40:34.650 --> 40:36.580
From now on, it'll all be good days.

40:37.060 --> 40:37.790
Cheers.

40:59.350 --> 41:00.100
Hello.

41:00.150 --> 41:01.110
Mr. Yang, what's wrong?

41:01.110 --> 41:02.070
Are you off work?

41:02.070 --> 41:02.960
Yes, I am.

41:03.150 --> 41:04.280
But don't worry.

41:04.380 --> 41:05.970
I've already made an appointment
with tomorrow's client.

41:05.970 --> 41:07.550
He'll come to the company in the afternoon
to go over the contract.

41:07.550 --> 41:08.070
Okay, okay.

41:08.070 --> 41:08.960
Stop talking.

41:09.190 --> 41:10.540
Come to the company tomorrow,

41:10.540 --> 41:12.420
hand over the clients you have,

41:12.440 --> 41:14.170
and don't come to work anymore.

41:14.330 --> 41:15.370
What do you mean?

41:15.400 --> 41:16.630
You're asking me?

41:16.880 --> 41:18.590
I've lost all my face because of you.

41:18.590 --> 41:19.800
The video of Mrs. Nie at the banquet

41:19.800 --> 41:21.880
talking about you being a mistress

41:21.880 --> 41:23.710
has already reached the clients.

41:23.710 --> 41:25.700
How dare you stay at the hotel?

41:25.800 --> 41:27.390
Don't you care about Yuhua's reputation?

41:27.390 --> 41:28.500
Come handle your resignation tomorrow.
